title: Stunning 2 Floor Family Duplex with 4 Bedrooms, Stained Glass Windows
posting_body: ['Beautiful family house ready to move in.', '- 4 Spacious Bedrooms with gorgeous hardwood flooring.', '-2 Bedrooms fit a king size bed comfortably, other two fit full size beds comfortably.', '- This beautiful duplex comes with 6 closets and 1 bathroom.', '-Kitchen leads to the refreshing patio in the back.', '-Located in Woodside near 7 Train (15 mins into NYC).', '-Spacious tile living room separate from kitchen.', '-Street parking available - very easy to find parking.', '-Stained Glass Windows.', '-Chandeliers.', '-Fireplace.', '-Outdoor Patio', '-Secure and peaceful neighborhood', '-2000', 'Sq ft', 'Please contact 347-322-1712 to schedule a viewing.']
